  "title": "Analyst (Multi-asset Portfolio)",
  "description": "<p>about the company</p><p>Our client is a leading global private bank.</p><p>about the job</p><ul><li>Manage and develop multi-asset strategies for clients</li><li>Conduct research of investment vehicles, as well as performance evaluation and risk analysis for multi-asset portfolios</li><li>Contribute to the development of investment views and how to execute them across various multi-asset portfolios</li><li>Collaborate with the Quant team in development of tools for management of multi-asset portfolio</li><li>This role requires someone who has at least 1 year of relevant experience in Equity or Multi-Asset portfolio research within the Investment Banking, Private Equity, Private Banking or Asset Management space.</li></ul><p>To apply online please use the 'apply' function.</p><p><strong>(EA: 94C3609/ R24124496)</strong></p>",
